      "widgets_values": ["PALETTE -> PROMPT PIPELINE\n\nTurns one reference image into a complete, validated Ideogram 4 prompt with the embedded palette, saved to ComfyUI/output.\n\nFlow: Load Image -> Extractor -> Override -> Palette->Global JSON -> Prompt Assembler -> JSON Validator -> Metadata Embedder.\n\nSet before running:\n  - Palette->Global JSON: aesthetics + lighting text\n  - Prompt Assembler 'base_json': your subject + medium\n  - Override: add/remove colors to hand-tweak the palette (optional)\n\nThe ShowText node is optional (needs ComfyUI-Custom-Scripts) and only displays the JSON.\nTo GENERATE an image, feed the Validator's prompt_json into your Ideogram generation node."],
